@page "/after-render-batch-applied-signal"

<h1>After Render Batch Applied Signal</h1>

<p>This page tests the <code>afterAllRenderBatchesApplied</code> JS event that fires every time
Blazor finishes applying a render batch to the DOM, enabling E2E tests to reliably detect
when interactive components have become active.</p>

<div>
    <ServerInteractiveCounter IncrementAmount="1" />
</div>
